{"tid":1598741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港欖球界世紀大戰","createTime":"2019-09-27T15:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T13:26:31.000Z","uid":149486,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5307a7d66cf6984b77ef8c880e94f5579d4e85f9","tid":1598741,"uid":149486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"10月5號紀律部隊會對警犬喺狗會3:00開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申:支持紀律部隊 但驚佢哋贏咗岀唔到門口 小心班狗無性<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkrugby.com/domestic/community-league-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrugby.com%2Fdomestic%2Fcommunity-league-1&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=de59ebdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkrugby.com/domestic/community-league-1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHxBGDF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHxBGDF.png&h=cca1bd83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f21234f96cc9b9fc7e0b9a221b24779a84cda12","tid":1598741,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"請幫忙廣傳，關乎運動存亡）<br />\n要盡快重新主導社會輿論導向，我哋而家要同政府鬥快！<br />\n<br />\n柒婆已經提晒水 運動層次要升級<br />\n唔獨立死路一條 共產黨唔會放過我地<br />\n<br />\n唔係「徹查警暴」，唔係「五大訴求」<br />\n而係「香港自治」呀屌你老母！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pv6u0U4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPv6u0U4.jpg&h=4d746acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 各位香港人，<br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔好再拘泥於五大訴求，乜你唔覺得同中共爭取呢啲嘢係一件好撚好笑嘅事咩？港共中共政府你都信，真係人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n<br />\n你爭取五大訴求，憑咩肯定中共唔會比假嘢你？假撤回果鑊過咗香港人一棟已經係最佳例子。<br />\n<br />\n大家醒下啦<br />\n事實係：中共只需要扮回應其中1-2個訴求，民意已經會逆轉<br />\n抗爭者就會少咗好大嘅民意基礎支持，向前線製造無力感就已經足以瓦解呢場運動。<br />\n<br />\n其實要求政府成立獨立調查委員會，係五大訴求裡面最撚戇鳩嘅一項。<br />\n咁樣做姐係白白將主導權落入港共政府手中，到時政府擺自己友入去又得，拖延時間又得，得咗。<br />\n沙中線豆腐渣獨立調查，鉛水事件獨立調查，有冇政府官員需要問責下台？<br />\n<br />\n話比你哋聽，成立獨立調查委員回只會製造機會比政府繼續作惡，逼害市民。<br />\n委員會真係可以避免同類事件再發生？Sorry, 乜你覺得真係做到？<br />\n<br />\n時機已經成熟 目標非常清晰<br />\n面對極權壓逼，推動香港自治係唯一嘅出路<br />\n我哋係呢個制度爭取唔到嘅嘢，我哋再建立一個政體嚟爭取<br />\n唔好話五大訴求，到時五百大訴求都可以爭取到<br />\n脫離中共魔掌，係拯救市民離開險境嘅唯一辦法<br />\n文革式清算批鬥已經殺到，我哋香港人已經無嘢可以輸<br />\n<br />\n經歷三個月港共政府殘殺市民，民怨沸騰底下<br />\n而家，已經係推動香港自治嘅最佳時機。<br />\n&ldquo;Remember, it's now or never&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81eP0Vb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81eP0Vb.jpg&h=24e401ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5J57NAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5J57NAf.jpg&h=2fdcff6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家嘅願景一係去實現<br />\n「港人治港，驅除共黨」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位加油！"},{"pid":"86be07e02dfa00bc632b835b8687112cb9e05523","tid":1598741,"uid":253266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"喺狗總打？仲入到去？"},{"pid":"75fccd481c35d168476570c75c7a294a8d3c3128","tid":1598741,"uid":149486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86be07e02dfa00bc632b835b8687112cb9e05523","tid":1598741,"uid":253266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"喺狗總打？仲入到去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T19:46:29.000Z","msg":"太子犬隻遊樂會"},{"pid":"9352aadeb8af110194ddce7ba73787d54818dfae","tid":1598741,"uid":39431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"